message.body: The social was okay. I was in a very crowded session today and I tried to sneak out to pee but I tripped on someone's bag and fell down in front of everyone.
My glasses went flying off my face
Thankfully not sick, just the cold weather. Making my bones ache! A hahajaja. Classic caitlin. (I said that out loud with a dumb voice)
Also I see that I misinterpreted the cold comment. Oops!
